rows.label: qst201516_msg0020
rows.name:
That must be the device carrying
the Thanatitan!

rows.label: qst201516_msg0021
rows.name: It's a lot bigger than I imagined...

rows.label: qst201516_msg0022
rows.name: And it seems it's already running...

rows.label: qst201516_msg0023
rows.name:
We must find the one responsible
and get them to stop it at once!

rows.label: qst201516_msg0024
rows.name:
The Gulan man is close, on the
far side of this floor.
